{"tid":479790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同一個台灣女生分別後 心情突然變到好失落","createTime":"2017-11-25T12:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T12:59:22.000Z","uid":72071,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bd940b97af1f5512ff10928af261408f8ce3cf","tid":479790,"uid":72071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"今次黎台灣幾日，終於搵到機會約見一個識左幾年既台灣朋友。<br />\n今日一齊玩左大半日，雖然中途佢既一個朋友都join埋，唔係全程都只得我地兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但今日都帶我行左好多地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直至到啱啱分別之後，由擰轉頭嗰刻起好似突然冇咗啲野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到依家心情都keep住係好down既情緒<br />\n<br />\n唔知係因為我唔捨得台灣妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係因為發現自己原來冇乜同歲數既朋友<br />\n<br />\n近排都開始發現自從返工以來，可以做返'自己'既時間，同埋Whatsapp入面既朋友訊息越黎少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想係手機搵個朋友去訴苦都無從入手咁。<br />\n<br />\n究竟我係因為咩原因而令到心情咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 社交圈子斷裂，求開解一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒L一見鐘情唔舍得台灣妹"}]}